# 3-Server Web Infrastructure

## Components
1. Load Balancer: HAProxy (Round Robin)
2. 2 Web Servers:
   - Nginx + App Server + Code + MySQL Replica

## Load Balancer
- Algorithm: Round Robin (rotates requests)
- Setup: Active-Active (both servers process traffic)

## Database: Primary-Replica
- Primary: Handles writes
- Replica: Handles reads (syncs from Primary)

## Issues
1. SPOF: Load balancer, database primary
2. Security: No firewall, no HTTPS
3. No monitoring or alerts
